qmOLTA">Tặng Thiên Mụ tự hoà thượng - 贈天姥寺和尚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Qu%E1%BA%BF/author-tVCgetl94ylIpxXT-wJP2g">Phan Quế</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-M%E1%BA%A1t-Nh%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3c/Th%E1%BA%ADp-nguy%E1%BB%87t-c%E1%BA%A3m-ho%C3%A0i-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-9EXk1UL_4fgPKp4w7146EQ">Thập nguyệt cảm hoài thi kỳ 1 - 十月感懷詩其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-M%E1%BA%A1t-Nh%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3c/author-QwHGtxwbcIXnt9ZJeL8mXw">Quách Mạt Nhược</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bang-B%E1%BA%A3n/Thi%C3%AAn-Quan-giang/poem-_BeccPVM3HGGrnQq91DzSA">Thiên Quan giang - 天關江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bang-B%E1%BA%A3n/author-s5no_WN-Qbyowo0KXT53Zg">Dương Bang Bản</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Th%E1%BB%A9-M%C3%ADnh-Vi%C3%AAn-Hu%E1%BB%B3nh-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-Nh%C3%A2m-Ng%E1%BB%8D-nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%91%C3%A1n-th%C3%AD-b%C3%BAt-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn-t%E1%BB%B1-thu%E1%BA%ADt/poem-NOsf_D5KplO2okBmQMlQZw">Thứ Mính Viên Huỳnh tiên sinh Nhâm Ngọ nguyên đán thí bút nguyên vận tự thuật - 次茗園黃先生壬午元旦試筆原韻自述</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br></div>	</div>
